des: "This is a perfectly flavored dip that is rich and creamy; serve warm with tortilla chips and your guests will be asking you for the recipe! Like it spicy? Add a jalapeno pepper!"
ins: Cook and stir Alfredo sauce and cream cheese together in a saucepan over medium heat until heated through and smooth, about 5 minutes. Stir butter, cilantro, green chile pepper, and garlic into sauce; cook and stir until heated through and smooth, about 5 minutes.
